energies you'll measure,

00:34:15.600 --> 00:34:17.550
it tells you the
probabilities with which

00:34:17.550 --> 00:34:20.670
you will measure energies.

00:34:20.670 --> 00:34:22.360
So they're the same thing.

00:34:22.360 --> 00:34:23.730
It's a very good question.

