00:55:02.920 --> 00:55:05.220
Where the raising
operator got its juice was

00:55:05.220 --> 00:55:09.356
from this computational
relation, a dagger with E

00:55:09.356 --> 00:55:14.310
was equal to h bar
omega a dagger.

00:55:14.310 --> 00:55:16.910
So can we build an
operator a dagger

00:55:16.910 --> 00:55:20.060
that raises states and
commutes with the energy

00:55:20.060 --> 00:55:21.760
operator in this fashion?

