00:55:24.810 --> 00:55:26.130
This is not a general property.

00:55:26.130 --> 00:55:29.330
This is not always
something we can do.

00:55:29.330 --> 00:55:32.140
If we could, then
that energy operator

00:55:32.140 --> 00:55:35.630
would have evenly spaced
energy eigenfunctions.

00:55:35.630 --> 00:55:39.120
On the other hand, it's
